<tr>
<td style="padding:2px 0;"><a href="/wiki/File:Stay,_Prince_and_hear.ogg" title="File:Stay, Prince and hear.ogg">Stay, Prince and hear</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<div id="ogg_player_7" style="width: 180px;">
